{"type": "article", "id": 15985, "title": "Roll collection", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-13T06:10:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141155TEX98ioMD4AGtzJp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自德国设计师 Verena Hennig 的椅子，包括凳子、长椅和带靠背的椅子三种。座位和靠背都是椭圆形的框架加竖条铝棒，配上两根弯曲的铝棍做腿，有简单的时尚感。它们真正的特别之处在于所有铝棒都是可滚动的，自带按摩功能，也增加了人和椅子的互动。有红、白、黑、米黄四种颜色，预计明年 1 月上市。<a href=\"http://www.hennigstore.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261434188psIBe4f10kSJ36d.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"675\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72115385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143419CjHE2tRxBd9iLs5m.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143419x5bfZYVHq87aCRv3.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143420v6QyIugsFKSf7Cbj.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"662\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70726496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}